        "archie:role": "section",
        "archie:order": 0,
        "body": {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "value": "The book opens as a herbal: a plant to a page, text flowing around the drawing. None of these plants can be named with certainty — some look observed, some invented — and the writing has never been read.",
          "format": "text/html",
          "purpose": "describing"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "https://micahchoo.github.io/Archie/viewer/published/voynich-reading/section/s2",
        "type": "Annotation",
        "motivation": "supplementing",
        "label": {
          "none": [
            "Astronomical"
          ]
        },
        "target": {
          "type": "SpecificResource",
          "source": "https://micahchoo.github.io/Archie/viewer/published/voynich-reading/canvas/o5",
          "selector": {
            "type": "FragmentSelector",
            "conformsTo": "http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/",
            "value": "xywh=pixel:400,300,4000,3100"
          }
        },
        "archie:role": "section",
        "archie:order": 1,
        "body": {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "value": "The pages widen into fold-out wheels of Sun, Moon, and stars, each star tied to a small labelled word. Conventional zodiac figures appear, but the labels around them stay closed to us.",
          "format": "text/html",
          "purpose": "describing"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "https://micahchoo.github.io/Archie/viewer/published/voynich-reading/section/s3",
        "type": "Annotation",
        "motivation": "supplementing",
        "label": {
          "none": [
            "Balneological"
          ]
        },
        "target": {
          "type": "SpecificResource",
          "source": "https://micahchoo.github.io/Archie/viewer/published/voynich-reading/canvas/o8",
          "selector": {
            "type": "FragmentSelector",
            "conformsTo": "http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/",
            "value": "xywh=pixel:200,400,2400,3000"
          }
        },
        "archie:role": "section",
        "archie:order": 2,
        "body": {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "value": "Small bathing figures move through green networks of pipes and basins. The script shifts character here — measurably a different system than the herbal — as if a second voice took up the pen.",
          "format": "text/html",
          "purpose": "describing"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "https://micahchoo.github.io/Archie/viewer/published/voynich-reading/section/s4",
        "type": "Annotation",
        "motivation": "supplementing",
        "label": {
          "none": [
            "Cosmological"
          ]
        },
        "target": {
          "type": "SpecificResource",
          "source": "https://micahchoo.github.io/Archie/viewer/published/voynich-reading/canvas/o9",
          "selector": {
            "type": "FragmentSelector",
            "conformsTo": "http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/",
            "value": "xywh=pixel:2600,2400,2800,2600"
          }
        },
        "archie:role": "section",
        "archie:order": 3,
        "body": {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "value": "The largest spread in the book unfolds into nine medallions joined by causeways, with castle-like and map-like forms. Whether it charts real places or imagined ones is part of what the page refuses to settle.",
          "format": "text/html",
          "purpose": "describing"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "https://micahchoo.github.io/Archie/viewer/published/voynich-reading/section/s5",
        "type": "Annotation",
        "motivation": "supplementing",
        "label": {
          "none": [
            "Pharmaceutical"
          ]
        },
        "target": {
          "type": "SpecificResource",
          "source": "https://micahchoo.github.io/Archie/viewer/published/voynich-reading/canvas/o10",
          "selector": {
            "type": "FragmentSelector",
            "conformsTo": "http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/",
            "value": "xywh=pixel:200,400,2300,3000"
          }
        },
        "archie:role": "section",
        "archie:order": 4,
        "body": {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "value": "Rows of labelled containers sit beside isolated roots and leaves — many of them tidier copies of plants from the opening herbal, as if assembled into a working reference.",
          "format": "text/html",
          "purpose": "describing"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "https://micahchoo.github.io/Archie/viewer/published/voynich-reading/section/s6",
        "type": "Annotation",
        "motivation": "supplementing",
        "label": {
          "none": [
            "Recipes"
          ]
        },
        "target": {
          "type": "SpecificResource",
          "source": "https://micahchoo.github.io/Archie/viewer/published/voynich-reading/canvas/o11",
          "selector": {
            "type": "FragmentSelector",
            "conformsTo": "http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/",
            "value": "xywh=pixel:200,160,2300,420"
          }
        },
        "archie:role": "section",
        "archie:order": 5,
        "body": {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "value": "The book closes on short starred paragraphs and, on its very last page, a few lines in ordinary Latin script — a later hand reaching in from outside the manuscript's silence.",
          "format": "text/html",
          "purpose": "describing"
        }
      }
    ],
